# Complexity Comparison

| Approach                | Time         | Space |
| ----------------------- | ------------ | ----- |
| Sorting                 | O(n log n)   | O(1)  |
| Min Heap                | O(n log k)   | O(k)  |
| Quick Select            | O(n) Average | O(1)  |
| Quick Select Worst Case | O(n²)        | O(1)  |
| 3-Way Quick Select      | O(n) Average | O(1)  |

